model.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
model.query:
SELECT
    $timeSeries as t,
    responseStatus,
    count()
FROM $table
WHERE $timeFilter and responseStatus != '200'
GROUP BY responseStatus, t
ORDER BY t
